title: #88 - Is La Croix Poison? BetterHelp & Kanye Meets Trump
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan and Hila address the BetterHelp controversy, drill into if La Croix is poison or not, examine Kanye's bizarre trip to the white house, talk about fat people riding donkeys, and smelling your own farts.
